The main interviewee: Judy Mikovits, is a former chronic fatigue researcher who has made controversial accusations against Dr. Anthony Fauci and has been involved in discrediting vaccines.
The filmmaker: Mikki Willis, sets a tone of conspiracy by claiming that Fauci was involved in a cover-up and has previously claimed that the novel coronavirus was intentionally released.
Mikovits asserts that the virus was mani: contradicting the scientific consensus that the exact origin of the coronavirus is not known.
